Revision history for Acme-CPANLists-PERLANCAR

0.16    2016-03-29 (PERLANCAR)

	- Add module list: Task::WorkingWithTree.

	- Remove mention of Class::Build::Array::Glob (the use of
	  Hook::AfterRuntime makes it problematic to load in some cases),
	  mention Class::Accessor::Array and Class::Accessor::Array::Glob.


0.15    2016-03-26 (PERLANCAR)

        - Add module lists: MooseStyleClassBuilder, NonMooseStyleClassBuilder,
          ArrayClassBuilder.


0.14    2016-03-16 (PERLANCAR)

	- Retired: Mention Carp::Always to boost its 'lcpan related-mods
          Carp::Always' ranking.

	- Avoided: Add more note about Exporter::Lite.

	- Add module lists: MagicVariableTechniques, Unbless, Weird.


0.13    2016-03-09 (PERLANCAR)

	- Wording/grammar.

	- [Bugfix] Fix wrong file name for
	  ::Task::PickingRandomLinesFromFile.


0.12    2016-03-09 (PERLANCAR)

	- Add JSON and JSON::XS to list of modules to avoid.


0.11    2016-02-25 (PERLANCAR)

	- Add Exporter::Lite to list of modules to avoid.


0.10    2016-02-20 (PERLANCAR)

        - Split each list into a separate module (POD) to help 'lcpan
          related-mods' result.

          When a POD document mentions unrelated modules together (which is when
          several unrelated lists are put together in a single POD), it gives a
          false positive for the 'lcpan related-mods' result which thinks that
          such modules are related. To help 'lcpan related-mods', I now put each
          list into a separate POD.

        - Add module list: Getting system-wide temporary directory in a portable
          way.

        - Add module list: Assertion.

        - Mention about BackPAN or GitHub on how to get retired modules.

        [REMOVED]

        - Remove test lists.


0.09    2016-01-23 (PERLANCAR)

	- Add module list: Retired modules.


0.08    2015-11-24 (PERLANCAR)

	- Add module list: Picking random lines from a file.


0.07    2015-10-29 (PERLANCAR)

	- Add module list: Ensuring only a single instance of program is
	  running.


0.06    2015-10-23 (PERLANCAR)

	- No functional changes.

	- [dist] Update prereq version to Acme::CPANLists 0.9.0 -> 0.90.1.


0.05    2015-10-23 (PERLANCAR)

	- Adjust to Acme::CPANLists specification v0.9.0.


0.04    2015-10-22 (PERLANCAR)

	- Add module lists: Modules I'm avoiding & Test list.


